<1ST_LINE>r a PM-NielsensList     12-07 0670</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-Nielsens List,0750</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>List of Week's Top-Rated TV Shows</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Nielsens</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
