<1ST_LINE>a e AM-APArts:Wasserman Adv12-1stLd-Writethru b0428 12-07 0891</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-AP Arts: Wasserman, Adv12-1st Ld-Writethru, b0428,0914</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv12</NOTE>
<NOTE>For Release Mon AMs, Dec 12 and Thereafter</NOTE>
<NOTE>Eds: SUBS 24th graf, ``Next, he'd like ...,'' to CORRECT that Yo
